data.description: Amazing opportunity to own this very well maintained home on one of the most sought after streets in Summergrove. Easy walk to clubhouse, tennis, swimming pool and pickleball. Highlights of this home include a recently renovated kitchen, in-law suite and picturesque lot with new landscaping and a welcoming circular driveway. 6 Bedrooms|4.5 Baths, welcoming two-story foyer, gourmet kitchen with new cabinets, appliances and quartz countertops, sunken formal living room, formal dining room, great room with soaring ceiling, floor to ceiling windows and cozy fireplace, primary bedroom on main level with in-suite bath - jetted tub, dual sinks, seperate shower and custom walk-in closet, walk-out access to large screened porch overlook the private backyard, newly renovated laundry room will have you wanting to do laundry. Second story features large bedrooms, each with jack and jill baths. Terrace level features bedroom, full bath, family room, full kitchen, large recreation room, workshop and patio. Outdoor features: large screened porch, grilling porch, and covered porch on lower level.
